Hello nice to work with you.

to make your project work you need :
    1 : setup the database by going to https://www.mongodb.com/fr then sign in and creat a cluster 
    2 : copy the cluster URI and past it in app.js line:23 (change my URI by yource).
    3 : if you want to creat a user, simply go to sign-up or navigate to localhost:3000/user/signup , creat a user ( be sure to fill all the fields) and enjoy. 
    4 : if you want to change a user to an admin you will need to access to your database, then change the value of isAdmin from 0 to 1
    5 : to add a new product , navigate to the dashboard , then add new product, and fill all field ( all fields are required ), and be sure to add a web picture URL in the iamge field
    6 : to review a product , you will have to : either buy a product, buy selecting a product then go to shopping card then order or 
    go to admin dashboard then manage products , then write a review .
    7 : all orders are stored in databases , you can see products history in /user/profile after login . 
    

i hope you like my product.
